<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<title>Engineering Excellence</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;600&display=swap');

  /* Reset and base */
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  body {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027, #203a43, #2c5364);
    color: #ffffff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  a {
    color: #58a6ff;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
  }
  a:hover {
    color: #82cfff;
  }

  /* Container */
  .container {
    width: 90%;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 2rem auto 4rem auto;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  /* Hero Section */
  header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 3rem 1rem 4rem;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top center, #1c92d2, #f2fcfe);
    color: #0a2435;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(28,146,210,0.6);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 1.2px;
  }
  header p {
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: #01314d;
  }
  header .hero-wave {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Engineering Cards Section */
  section.cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  .card {
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #3a7bd5, #00d2ff);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.4);
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.7);
  }
  .card svg {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    fill: #e0f7ff;
  }
  .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }
  .card p {
    font-weight: 300;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* Dynamic Interactive Section */
  section.dynamic {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    background: linear-gradient(145deg, #232526, #1c1c1c);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: #58a6ff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(88,166,255,0.5);
  }
  section.dynamic h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  section.dynamic p {
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .gear-container {
    display: inline-block;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  svg.gear {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    fill: #58a6ff;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px #58a6ff80);
  }
  .gear-container:hover svg.gear {
    transform: rotate(360deg);
    fill: #82cfff;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px #82cfffcc);
  }

  /* Footer */
  footer {
    background: #0a2435;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #65879f;
    box-shadow: inset 0 1px 3px #0e3a5a;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    section.dynamic h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>Engineering Excellence</h1>
    <p>Exploring the frontier of innovation, design, and sustainable solutions.</p>
    <svg class="hero-wave" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path fill="#0a2435" fill-opacity="1" d="M0,160L48,165.3C96,171,192,181,288,192C384,203,480,213,576,213.3C672,213,768,203,864,165.3C960,128,1056,64,1152,53.3C1248,43,1344,85,1392,106.7L1440,128L1440,320L1392,320C1344,320,1248,320,1152,320C1056,320,960,320,864,320C768,320,672,320,576,320C480,320,384,320,288,320C192,320,96,320,48,320L0,320Z"></path>
    </svg>
  </header>

  <main class="container">
    <section class="cards" aria-label="Engineering Fields">
      <article class="card" tabindex="0" aria-describedby="mech-desc">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M32 12 L32 52 M12 32 L52 32" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="10" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Mechanical Engineering</h3>
        <p id="mech-desc">Designing and manufacturing mechanical systems for motion, energy, and power solutions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" tabindex="0" aria-describedby="elec-desc">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" >
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="28" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
          <polyline points="20 32 28 20 36 44 44 32" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <line x1="20" y1="32" x2="44" y2="32" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4"/>
        </svg>
        <h3>Electrical Engineering</h3>
        <p id="elec-desc">Developing electrical systems and circuits powering modern technology.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" tabindex="0" aria-describedby="civil-desc">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <rect x="20" y="20" width="24" height="24" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none" />
          <path d="M20 32 H44" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
          <path d="M32 20 V44" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
        </svg>
        <h3>Civil Engineering</h3>
        <p id="civil-desc">Planning, designing, and constructing infrastructure for better living.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" tabindex="0" aria-describedby="soft-desc">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <rect x="18" y="22" width="28" height="20" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none" rx="2"/>
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="8" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
          <path d="M24 32 L40 32" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
        </svg>
        <h3>Software Engineering</h3>
        <p id="soft-desc">Building applications and systems that drive digital transformation.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card" tabindex="0" aria-describedby="chem-desc">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="20" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" fill="none"/>
          <line x1="12" y1="44" x2="52" y2="20" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
          <line x1="20" y1="12" x2="44" y2="52" stroke="#b5e0ff" stroke-width="4" />
        </svg>
        <h3>Chemical Engineering</h3>
        <p id="chem-desc">Innovating processes to transform raw materials into valuable products.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="dynamic" aria-label="Interactive Gear">
      <h2>Explore Engineering Dynamics</h2>
      <p>Hover over the gear below to see dynamic rotational motion, symbolizing the endless innovation in engineering.</p>
      <div class="gear-container" role="img" aria-label="Rotating gear">
        <svg class="gear" viewBox="0 0 512 512" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false">
          <path d="M487.4 315.7l-42.5-24.5v-45.2l42.5-24.5c3.3-1.9 4.7-5.8 3.3-9.3l-40.6-93.4c-1.6-3.7-6-5.2-9.7-3.3l-42.1 24.2-39.2-22.6v-48.1c0-4.4-3.6-7.7-8-7.7h-91c-4.4 0-8 3.3-8 7.7v48.1l-39.3 22.6-42.1-24.2c-3.7-1.9-8 0-9.6 3.3l-40.6 93.4c-1.4 3.5 0 7.5 3.3 9.3l42.5 24.5v45.3l-42.5 24.6c-3.3 1.9-4.7 5.8-3.3 9.3l40.6 93.4c1.6 3.7 6 5.2 9.7 3.3l42.1-24.2 39.2 22.6v48.1c0 4.4 3.6 7.7 8 7.7h91c4.4 0 8-3.3 8-7.7v-48.1l39.3-22.6 42.1 24.2c3.7 1.9 8 0 9.6-3.3l40.6-93.4c1.4-3.5 0-7.5-3.3-9.3zM256 322.4c-36.5 0-66.1-29.6-66.1-66 0-36.4 29.6-66 66.1-66 36.4 0 66 29.6 66 66 0 36.4-29.6 66-66 66z"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2024 Engineering Excellence. Crafted with passion for innovation.
  </footer>
</body>
</html>

<script>
  // Optional: Add interactivity to the gear
  document.querySelector('.gear-container').addEventListener('click', () => {
    alert('Keep innovating!');
  });